Note: The individual Argonaut questionnaire profiles identify the structural constraints, terminology bindings and invariants, however, implementers must refer to the conformance requirements for details on the RESTful operations, specific profiles and the search parameters applicable to each of the Argonaut questionnaire actors.</p>\n			<h3 id=\"conformance-requirements-for-the-argonaut-questionnaire-implementation-guide-answerbank\">Conformance requirements for the Argonaut questionnaire Implementation Guide Answer-Bank Server</h3>\n			<ul>\n				<li>FHIR Version: 3.0.1</li>\n				<li>Supported formats: xml, json</li>\n				<li>Published: May 20, 2018</li>\n				<li>Published by: The Argonaut Project</li>\n			</ul>\n			<p>The Section describes the expected Capabilities of the Argonaut Answer-Bank Server which is responsible for providing responses to the requests submitted by the Argonaut questionnaire clients (Form Author/Editor and Provider EHRs). The complete list of FHIR profiles, RESTful operations, and search parameters supported by Argonaut questionnaire Answer-Banks are defined.</p>\n			<h4 id=\"behavior\">Behavior</h4>\n			<p>Description:</p>\n			<p>The Argonaut questionnaire Answer-Bank <strong>SHALL (...todo... review...)</strong>:</p>\n			<ol>\n				<li>Support at least one Argonaut questionnaireuse case.</li>\n				<li>Implement the RESTful behavior according to the FHIR specification including returning the appropriate response classes as described in the FHIR specification for <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3//http.html\">FHIR RESTful API</a> and <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3//operations.html\">Extended Operations on the RESTful API</a>.</li>\n				<li>Conform to the <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/1.0.1\">US Core Implementation Guiide</a>.</li>\n				<li>Support <em>json</em> resource formats for all Argonaut questionnaire interactions.</li>\n				<li>Declare a CapabilityStatement identifying the list of profiles, operations, search parameter supported.</li>\n			</ol>\n			<p>The Argonaut questionnaire Answer-Bank <strong>SHOULD (...todo... review...)</strong>:</p>\n			<ol>\n				<li>Support <em>xml</em> resource formats for all Argonaut questionnaire interactions.</li>\n				<li>Identify the Argonaut questionnaire profiles supported as part of the FHIR <code>meta.profile</code> attribute for each instance.</li>\n			</ol>\n			<h4 id=\"security-\">Security:</h4>\n			<p>For general security consideration refer to the <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/security.html\">Security section</a> in the US Core Implementation Guide.</p>\n			<h4 id=\"profile-interaction-summary-\">Profile Interaction Summary: (...todo... review...)</h4>\n			<h4 id=\"resource-details-\">Resource  Details: (...todo... review...)</h4>\n			<hr/>\n		</div>"
